          </a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="/new-hampshire/hikes/4000-footer" class="hover:text-emerald-400 transition flex items-center gap-2">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-emerald-400" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M14 6l-3.75 5 2.85 3.8-1.6 1.2C9.81 13.75 7 10 7 10l-6 8h22L14 6z"/>
            </svg>
            4000 Footers
          </a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="/new-hampshire/hikes/dog-friendly" class="hover:text-emerald-400 transition flex items-center gap-2">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-amber-400" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M4.5 12c-.83 0-1.5-.67-1.5-1.5S3.67 9 4.5 9 6 9.67 6 10.5 5.33 12 4.5 12zm3-4C6.67 8 6 7.33 6 6.5S6.67 5 7.5 5 9 5.67 9 6.5 8.33 8 7.5 8zm5-1c-.83 0-1.5-.67-1.5-1.5S11.67 4 12.5 4s1.5.67 1.5 1.5S13.33 7 12.5 7zm4 1c-.83 0-1.5-.67-1.5-1.5S15.67 5 16.5 5s1.5.67 1.5 1.5S17.33 8 16.5 8zm1.5 4c0-.83.67-1.5 1.5-1.5s1.5.67 1.5 1.5-.67 1.5-1.5 1.5-1.5-.67-1.5-1.5zm-8 6.5c0 1.66-1.34 3-3 3s-3-1.34-3-3c0-1.3.84-2.4 2-2.82V9.71C6.28 9.9 6 10.42 6 11c0 .55.45 1 1 1h1c.55 0 1-.45 1-1 0-.58-.28-1.1-.72-1.29V15.18c1.16.42 2 1.52 2 2.82z"/>
            </svg>
